name: IsThereSewageInTheChicagoRiver
0:
”Alexa, ask chicago c. s. o. status if is there sewage in the Chicago River right now”
”tell me if there is sewage in the Chicago River”
”give me the current cso status for the Chicago River”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chicago c. s. o. status
des:
When Chicago experiences significant rain or snowmelt, the Chicagoland water management agencies must dump excess wastewater into the lake and river to prevent flooding. These systems are called combined sewer overflows (CSO).

This Alexa Skill reports whether sewage is currently being dumped into the Chicago River.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
